Game Design Document

Name: Bulls and Cows

Purpose/Goal:

Review C++ coding constructs.
Learn Unreal Coding style as per their guide.
Get a grasp of OO programming towards an app development.


Concept and Rules:

Guess the ISOGRAM game.
Isogram implies a word without repeating letters.
Limited number of guesses.
After each guess
Bulls: right letter at right place
Cows: right letter wrong place

Requirements:

Input: 
Length of the word to be guessed.
Letters/words of the predefined length.
Outputs: Messages regarding:
Bulls and Cows
Error messages
Help messages
Hints??
